ENGINE START

main types:
struct Entity
struct Space
struct Engine
struct BearClass

relation to game:
"game class" inherits from BearClass and
creates an Engine object 
"game class" has callbacks (init, update etc) called by the engine object

ENGINE END

GAME START

             engine
main() => "game class" => big switch =>
{ MENU, PLAY }
PLAY => run code for current level
MENU => run code for menu

GAME END